Plan Your Time
Each week, on Wednesday, you will get access to a new module with video lectures and corresponding assignments.
Complete all assignments, discussions, and quizzes for the week before the due date, which is no later than 
Wednesday at 04:29 PM (UTC) of the following week. 
Live sessions (webinars) and office hours have been scheduled throughout the course journey to help you interact 
with your mentors and Learning Facilitators. For details of the webinar schedule, please refer to the Live Sessions page. 
